<p>Why did ravana (brahmin) was killed by Rama?</p>
<p>Shiv purana - shiv killed Brahma and his son.&nbsp;</p>
<ol>
<li>Because they were not hermit householder , did not renounce desire.&nbsp;</li>
<li>Like Buddhism, the concept is renunciation of desire. Even in Hindi mythology</li></ol>
